-- ftd.column:
width: fill-container
padding-horizontal.px: 50
padding-horizontal.px if {ftd.device == "mobile"}: 20
background.solid: $inherited.colors.background.base


-- pd.package: Rubik Iso Devnagari - fastn font
name: jahanvir.github.io/rubik-font

This component consist of Rubik Iso font with all it's styles.


-- pd.component: Rubik Iso - fastn font
name: https://github.com/jahanvir/rubik-font

This component consist of Rubik Iso font with all it's styles from Thin-100 to Black-900.



-- pd.hidden-code: How to use

include fifthtry.github.io/rubik-font package into FASTN.ftd file

\-- fastn.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/rubik-font/assets as rubik

\-- fastn.auto-import: rubik

Inside your .ftd file to change for any specific token use:

\-- fastn.type.headline-small.font: $rubik.fonts.Rubik-Iso

\-- ftd.text:
role: $fastn.type.headline-small


